                        <interp inst="t18760626-name-211" type="surname" value="BUTCHER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18760626-name-211" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES BUTCHER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). I get this other bill (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) from a public-house in Buckingham Palace Road—Williams can tell you all about that.</p>
